            "content_html": "<p>En esta documentaci√≥n encontrar√°s el paso a paso de la creaci√≥n de esta aplicaci√≥n.<br><br></p>\n<p>Prompts:</p>\n<p>1.Clona esta app lo m√°ximo posible (Foto)</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"505\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/1-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/1-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/1-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/1-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>2. Crea un inicio de sesi√≥n y registro para poder tener una cuenta propia.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"511\" height=\"522\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/2-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/2-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/2-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/2-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>3. Creame los niveles de Duolingo, quiero que haya un selector de idioma para poder aprender independientemente cada idioma. Tambien una parte de perfil para poder ver el progreso y cambiar el modo dia/noche y poder cerrar sesion</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"287\" height=\"537\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3-lg.png 1024w\"></figure><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal); outline: 3px solid rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb), 0.55) !important;\" src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/3.3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"270\" height=\"537\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3.3-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3.3-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3.3-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/3.3-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>4.Vamos a utilizar esta imagen para el inicio de sesion. Tambien quiero que haya una base de datos en el que los usuarios pueden registrarse y poder utilizar su cuenta desde cualquier dispositivo (Me recomendo firebase).</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"241\" height=\"391\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/4-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/4-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/4-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/4-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>5.Quiero un centro de pr√°ctica donde hara cartas de aprendizaje y tambien relacionar las palabras, con sus efectos corresponiendtes.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"286\" height=\"527\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/5-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/5-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/5-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/5-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>6.Quiero que haya banderas en los idiomas</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"623\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/6-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/6-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/6-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/6-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>7.Quiero transiciones al entrar a un nivel.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"910\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/7-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/7-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/7-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/7-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>8.Quiero un sistema de perfil con avatares y biografia, tambien de seguidores y seguidos, en el que escribes el nombre de usuario y puedas seguirlo.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"471\" height=\"943\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/8-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/8-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/8-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/8-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>9.Pon un sistema de divisiones y ascensos como en el duolingo, en el que todas las cuentas creadas compitan.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"928\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/9-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/9-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/9-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/9-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>10.Pon un contador para las vidas al fallar niveler (1min).</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"47\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/10-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/10-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/10-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/7/responsive/10-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/indexClon5.html\">Link a la aplicaci√≥n</a></p>",
