            "title": "Manual de Configuraci√≥n Inicial Raspberry Pi y Mac mini.",
            "summary": "Sigue estos pasos para dejar listos los equipos Raspberry Pi y Mac&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"post__toc\">\n<h3>Indice</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf3fq04t\">Configuraci√≥n de Raspberry Pi</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf6oiu5i\">Pantalla de Bienvenida</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm84\">Elegir WiFi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm85\">Clave WiFi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm86\">Actualizar Sistema</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm87\">Nuevo Usuario</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm88\">Navegador Web</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf3fq04u\">Configuraci√≥n de Mac mini</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm89\">Crear Cuenta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mcetoc_1jatf8snm8a\">Listo para usar</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>Sigue estos pasos para dejar listos los equipos Raspberry Pi y Mac mini.</p>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<h4 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf3fq04t\">Configuraci√≥n de Raspberry Pi</h4>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/51omP97I7AL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"487\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/51omP97I7AL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/51omP97I7AL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/51omP97I7AL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/51omP97I7AL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"15\">\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf6oiu5i\" data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\"><strong>Pantalla de Bienvenida</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,0,0\"><span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">Ver√°s el escritorio de la Pi. Haz clic en </span><strong style=\"font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit;\">'Next'</strong><span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">. Nota: Si el sistema necesita configurar el Bluetooth, se reiniciar√° solo.</span></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.30_59c3a018.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.30_59c3a018-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.30_59c3a018-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.30_59c3a018-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.30_59c3a018-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n<p>¬†</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm84\" data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\"><strong>Elegir WiFi</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,1,0\">Busca la red <strong>'WiFi_AULA_ATECA'</strong> en la lista y contin√∫a.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.24_1c32cfa3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.24_1c32cfa3-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.24_1c32cfa3-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.24_1c32cfa3-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.24_1c32cfa3-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm85\" data-path-to-node=\"15,2,0\"><strong>Clave WiFi</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,2,0\">¬†Escribe la contrase√±a de la red seleccionada y pulsa <strong>'Next'</strong>.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_c4295392.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_c4295392-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_c4295392-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_c4295392-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_c4295392-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm86\" data-path-to-node=\"15,3,0\"><strong>Actualizar Sistema</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,3,0\">Aqu√≠ puedes actualizar el software pulsando <strong>'Next'</strong> o saltarlo con <strong>'Skip'</strong>. Lo mas recomendable es actualizarlo.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.22_8009cb02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.22_8009cb02-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.22_8009cb02-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.22_8009cb02-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.22_8009cb02-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm87\" data-path-to-node=\"15,4,0\"><strong>Nuevo Usuario</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,4,0\">Define el nombre de usuario y la contrase√±a que usar√°s en la Raspberry.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.25_adfdc50c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.25_adfdc50c-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.25_adfdc50c-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.25_adfdc50c-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.25_adfdc50c-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm88\" data-path-to-node=\"15,5,0\"><strong>Navegador Web</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"15,5,0\">Elige <strong>Firefox</strong> como tu navegador por defecto. Puedes marcar la casilla para desinstalar Chromium si no vas a usarlo.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_95a20531.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_95a20531-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_95a20531-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_95a20531-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.23_95a20531-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"16\">¬†</p>\n<h4 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf3fq04u\">Configuraci√≥n de Mac mini</h4>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/111894_macminihero.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"317\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/111894_macminihero-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/111894_macminihero-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/111894_macminihero-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/111894_macminihero-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"17\">\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm89\" data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\"><strong>Crear Cuenta</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,0,0\">Rellena los datos para el usuario local (nombre real, nombre de cuenta y contrase√±a).</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.46_90b8e069.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.46_90b8e069-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.46_90b8e069-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.46_90b8e069-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.46_90b8e069-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h5 id=\"mcetoc_1jatf8snm8a\" data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\"><strong>Listo para usar</strong></h5>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"17,1,0\">Una vez creada la cuenta, acceder√°s directamente al escritorio de macOS.</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.44_a9ad3ee4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"461\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.44_a9ad3ee4-xs.jpg 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.44_a9ad3ee4-sm.jpg 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.44_a9ad3ee4-md.jpg 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/6/responsive/Imagen-de-WhatsApp-2025-11-20-a-las-19.42.44_a9ad3ee4-lg.jpg 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>",
