            "summary": "Esta documentaci√≥n se encontraran los prompts y paso a paso de la&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Esta documentaci√≥n se encontraran los prompts y paso a paso de la creacion de esta app.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"1,0,0\"><strong>Petici√≥n inicial:</strong> Actuar como experto en HTML/CSS/JS puro y crear una aplicaci√≥n tipo \"gu√≠a\" (sobre un pueblo, pel√≠culas, etc.) con modo oscuro, tarjetas y transiciones.<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1186\" height=\"404\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/1-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/1-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/1-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/1-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"1,1,0\"><strong>Definir contenido:</strong> Concretar la informaci√≥n: Gu√≠a sobre <strong>Pinto</strong> y una lista de <strong>10 pel√≠culas favoritas</strong> (tipo Alien, Expediente Warren).<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1352\" height=\"584\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/2-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/2-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/2-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/2-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"1,3,0\"><strong>Dise√±o dos columnas:</strong> Cambiar la estructura a dos columnas (Pinto vs Pel√≠culas), a√±adir <strong>degradados direccionales</strong> espec√≠ficos (flechas negra y verde) y efecto de movimiento en la imagen al pasar el rat√≥n.<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1166\" height=\"720\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/3-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/3-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/3-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/3-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"1,5,0\"><strong>Ajuste de tarjetas:</strong> Hacer las <strong>columnas m√°s altas</strong>, im√°genes m√°s grandes que cubran el fondo y evitar espacios blancos al hacer hover. Aqui ya pas√© de hacer una guia de pinto y me centre en las peliculas<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1407\" height=\"919\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/4-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/4-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/4-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/4-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-path-to-node=\"1,9,0\"><strong>Detalle completo (El gran cambio):</strong> Pedir que se muestren las <strong>puntuaciones, estrellas, sinopsis y opiniones</strong> con un dise√±o de tarjeta detallada (basado en tu captura), en lugar de la lista de texto simple que ten√≠amos.<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1383\" height=\"950\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/5-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/5-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/5-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/5-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n</li>\n<li><strong> Enriquecimiento de datos y expansi√≥n de contenido</strong> \"Utilizando la nueva API (OMDb), ampl√≠a la base de datos local a√±adiendo m√°s categor√≠as de g√©nero y pel√≠culas en cada una. Adem√°s, implementa una llamada a la API para obtener descripciones (sinopsis) m√°s detalladas din√°micamente, manteniendo la estructura de c√≥digo unificado.\"<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1470\" height=\"948\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/6-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/6-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/6-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/6-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></li>\n<li><strong> Enriquecimiento de datos y expansi√≥n de contenido</strong> \"Utilizando la nueva API (OMDb), ampl√≠a la base de datos local a√±adiendo m√°s categor√≠as de g√©nero y pel√≠culas en cada una. Adem√°s, implementa una llamada a la API para obtener descripciones (sinopsis) m√°s detalladas din√°micamente, manteniendo la estructura de c√≥digo unificado.\"<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/7.1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1401\" height=\"922\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/7.1-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/7.1-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/7.1-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/7.1-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></li>\n<li>Los demas prompts son arreglos visuales o de bugs y hacerlo multiplataforma<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"814\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/8-xs.png 300w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/8-sm.png 480w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/8-md.png 768w ,https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/media/posts/5/responsive/8-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></li>\n</ol>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://narcisx.github.io/2damdi/indexCinemalist.html\">Click aqui para ver la app</a></p>",
